# Linguist overrides for GitHub language statistics
# See: https://github.com/github/linguist/blob/master/docs/overrides.md

# ============================================
# EXCLUDE from language statistics
# ============================================

# Template files are DATA (generated output patterns), not operational code
# They should not count toward repository language statistics
templates/** linguist-vendored
*.tmpl linguist-vendored

# Pattern and knowledge files are data/configuration
patterns/** linguist-vendored
knowledge/** linguist-vendored
blueprints/** linguist-vendored

# Example files are documentation
*.example linguist-documentation

# Test fixtures are not primary source code
tests/fixtures/** linguist-vendored

# ============================================
# INCLUDE in language statistics (operational code)
# ============================================

# Python is the operational language of this repository
*.py linguist-language=Python linguist-detectable

# Markdown documentation
*.md linguist-documentation
